{"tid":1606194,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"101 黃大仙討論","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T13:57:20.000Z","uid":24390,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a2bf4c6547d92eea556bdbdcccfcc0de28cfd3e","tid":1606194,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:32:33.000Z","msg":"聽日黃大仙區1330集合之後一定唔可以冇target<br />\n黃大仙除咗狗屋同狗舍就得返民政事務處同社會福利署，冇咩明確目標（有錯請指出）<br />\n合適嘅target要去到klb,kt燈柱/出tst<br />\n唔太覺得淨圍狗舍有太大作用，加上要keep住流動先唔會被trap<br />\n大家有咩意見"},{"pid":"78094267851682452d1e90810275c1b7cd4afd61","tid":1606194,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"聽日一點，200萬人去銅鑼灣<br />\n東角道集合，遊行至中環，唔好遲到！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190930/60101614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60101614&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6s4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=ae922ed9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60101614&h=01f19774\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190930/60101614</a>"},{"pid":"0af951d5ab109a4cdcbe9f99d6416043ea8f67b1","tid":1606194,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:33:58.000Z","msg":"前線一定去港島<br />\n記者、First Aid 分散六區<br />\n點解要咁做?"},{"pid":"fd162a518becb637f70742186f649fd8c218f99b","tid":1606194,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78094267851682452d1e90810275c1b7cd4afd61","tid":1606194,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"聽日一點，200萬人去銅鑼灣<br />\n東角道集合，遊行至中環，唔好遲到！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190930/60101614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60101614&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6s4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=ae922ed9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60101614&h=01f19774\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190930/60101614</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"我知人數好緊要，但係我更加支持開花"},{"pid":"9b4d12b46b5b2b4cea5f9f346227d2a3d92f431a","tid":1606194,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"去港島"},{"pid":"b5462fdb3cd9bf5745bc5e71af84a2569bdfc6e9","tid":1606194,"uid":182687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"34f9287999bfa0eb9e4afb649c7ec8b8985bd3f7","tid":1606194,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:35:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日出去前睇左先</span></span></span><br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..</span></span><br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..</span></span><br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n一班CSD職員上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGBrHN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGBrHN5.jpg&h=abebdb5d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jffTnN9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjffTnN9.jpg&h=e9b627a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6126bb408c54ad2045db00b529d50d9f18e64f4f","tid":1606194,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:36:49.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0076896afd2da51d36d3a8647477b1be2c96e960","tid":1606194,"uid":24390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b4d12b46b5b2b4cea5f9f346227d2a3d92f431a","tid":1606194,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:35:17.000Z","msg":"去港島"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"港島已經試過好多次，對方重防根本冇得打"},{"pid":"4124dfcd693ee2780580d30b80c2e6239a66c3b5","tid":1606194,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd162a518becb637f70742186f649fd8c218f99b","tid":1606194,"uid":24390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78094267851682452d1e90810275c1b7cd4afd61","tid":1606194,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:33:16.000Z","msg":"聽日一點，200萬人去銅鑼灣<br />\n東角道集合，遊行至中環，唔好遲到！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190930/60101614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60101614&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6s4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=ae922ed9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190930%2F60101614&h=01f19774\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190930/60101614</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:34:41.000Z","msg":"我知人數好緊要，但係我更加支持開花"},"citedBy":1,